  - display-strategy-selection: Selected decimal-pack for screen __inline_show_39_0.
  - display-current-x-reuse: Reused clue already in X as the first field of screen __inline_show_39_0.
  - packed-display-lowering: Display __inline_show_39_0 may use display-byte encodings in later layout passes.
  - single-use-rule-inline: Inlined single-use rule reveal_safe_cell at line 30.
  - terminal-branch-end-elision: Omitted unreachable if-end jump after terminal then branch at line 26.
  - bit-mask-helper: Emitted shared bit_mask helper using __bit_mask_shared with quotient reuse.
  - spatial-hit-bit-mask-helper-reuse: Reused shared bit_mask helper __bit_mask_0 inside spatial hit __spatial_hit_mines.
  - shared-straight-line-helper: Extracted 1 straight-line helper from 6 repeated body occurrences (7 cells saved).
  - store-recall-peephole: Dropped 2 redundant П->X immediately after X->П to the same register.
  - dead-store-elimination: Removed 1 store(s) to register(s) never read before the next assignment.
  - constant-folding: Dropped 1 identity arithmetic operation(s) (0+ or 1*).
  - preloaded-indirect-flow: Activated post-layout: replaced 18 direct branch/call(s) with proven preloaded indirect flow.
  - dark-entry-layout: Pointed 2 branch(es) at an executable suffix through a proven dark-entry formal address (beyond the 104-cell window).
  - constants-dual-use: Shared 1 duplicate selector register(s): one stored constant now drives several dispatch sites, freeing the rest.
  - generated-setup-program: Generated optimized setup program for mines.
  - setup-duplicate-preload-store-reuse: Loaded setup constant 0 once and stored it into R1, R9.
  - setup-int-random-range-lowering: Lowered int(random() * 999) without К [x] so the MK-61 random sequence keeps moving.
  - shared-bit-mask-helper-layout: Selected shared bit_mask helper calls after full layout (81 vs 93 cells).

